Sidebar layout for read_delim module

These functions return the ui elements for a side panel and a main panel.

read_delim_sidebar_side(id)

read_delim_sidebar_main(id)

Arguments

id
character, used to identify a namespace

Value

a shiny::tagList containing UI elements

Details

Generally, the side elements are the inputs; the main elements are the outputs.

See also

Other read_delim module functions: read_delim_server, read_delim_ui_input, read_delim_ui_misc, read_delim_ui_output

Examples

library("shiny")
shinyUI(
  fluidPage(
    shinyjs::useShinyjs(),
    sidebarLayout(
      sidebarPanel(read_delim_sidebar_side("foo")),
      mainPanel(read_delim_sidebar_main("foo"))
    )
  )
)
